location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Single source of truth: appVersionBase in gradle.properties holds major.minor. buildNumber is the CI run number passed via -PbuildNumber. versionName = appVersionBase.buildNumber, versionCode = 100 + buildNumber. This ensures the published release tag and APK embedded versionName always match."}, {"id": "wardove_release_signing", "label": "Release Signing Strategy (stable keystore)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A changing keystore key causes App not installed errors during in-app updates. signingConfigs.release reads KEYSTORE_PATH, KEYSTORE_PASSWORD, KEY_ALIAS, KEY_PASSWORD from environment. Falls back to debug key when KEYSTORE_PATH is unset (local builds, fork PRs)."}, {"id": "wardove_no_retrofit_rationale", "label": "No Retrofit: HttpURLConnection Used Directly", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "UpdateRepository uses java.net.HttpURLConnection directly for the GitHub API call instead of Retrofit, keeping the dependency footprint minimal for a single API endpoint."}, {"id": "wardove_desugaring_rationale", "label": "Core Library Desugaring (java.time APIs on minSdk 24)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "coreLibraryDesugaringEnabled = true enables java.time APIs on Android 7.0 (minSdk 24) which natively only supports them from API 26+."}, {"id": "wardove_calendar_screen", "label": "Calendar Screen (top-level drawer nav screen)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "au